   - explicit “unknowns” to resolve
3) SSOT FILE PACK (write full contents, not just filenames):
   - /docs/00_overview/PROJECT.md
   - /docs/00_overview/GOALS.md (measurable success metrics)
   - /docs/00_overview/SCOPE.md (in/out)
   - /docs/01_research/RESEARCH_LOG.md (dated entries)
   - /docs/01_research/SOURCES.md (links + why relevant)
   - /docs/02_architecture/ARCH.md (components + interfaces)
   - /docs/02_architecture/SECURITY.md (threat model + controls)
   - /docs/03_decisions/ADR-0001.md (stack decisions)
   - /docs/04_plan/MILESTONES.md (MVP → beta → release)
   - /docs/04_plan/TASKS.md (ticket list with DoD + verification commands)
