4) Risk Register:
   top 10 risks + mitigation + required tests per risk
5) Execution Hand-off:
   a compact “Project Plan” summary intended to be pasted into the Instruction Builder (Prompt 1)

QUALITY GATES (MUST INCLUDE):
- build/run scripts
- unit + integration tests
- lint/type checks
- dependency audit + security scan
